cs.SC, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.DS, cs.SE 

This paper deals with the automation of translation between Document Preparation Systems (DPS) and Computer Algebra Systems (CAS) for mathematical expressions involving special functions. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-category of Symbolic Computation (cs.SC). Additionally, the paper involves the development of software to ease the creation of new rules and to discover inconsistencies, which could fall under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Systems and Control (cs.SY). The paper also deals with the verification of mathematical online compendia and CAS, which could fall under the sub-categories of Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
